snippet.title: Mario Kart Tour - Trailer
snippet.description:
【Mario Kart Tour】
Available on September 25
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1293634699
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.zaka

Follow along for an app introduction and the latest information.

For more information, visit the official website for detail.

ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with In-game Purchases

USK ab 0 Jahren (Onlinekäufe)
